text: Neohebestola humeralis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Blanchard in 1851. It is known from Chile.BioLib.cz - Neohebestola humeralis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Forsteriini Category:Beetles described in 1851
